				questions
			QUIT	Quit replacing

		Off means that it automagically replaces ALL ocurrences

You are also presented with two more inputfields (compared to those when
searching). You are supposed to type in the string to replace WITH here.
The four inputfields are named "S-ASC", "S-HEX", "R-ASC" and "R-HEX",
where "S" stands for "Search" and "R" for "Replace". Just press <Enter>
to start searching for matches to replace.

